@startuml sequence_detailed
title Detailed Sequence Diagram - Parking Reservation and Payment

actor User
participant "Mobile App / Kiosk UI" as UI
participant "Backend System" as Backend
database "Parking Database" as DB
participant "Sensor/Camera System" as Sensor
participant "Payment Gateway" as Payment

User -> UI: Open app and request available spaces
UI -> Backend: Get available parking spaces
Backend -> Sensor: Request live occupancy data
Sensor --> Backend: Send occupancy and entry/exit data
Backend -> Backend: Validate and normalize sensor data
Backend -> DB: Read parking space records
DB --> Backend: Return available spaces
Backend --> UI: Send available spaces
UI --> User: Display available spaces

alt Space available
  User -> UI: Select parking space
  UI -> Backend: Reserve parking space
  Backend -> DB: Check space availability
  DB --> Backend: Space available
  Backend -> DB: Save reservation and create session
  DB --> Backend: Reservation saved
  Backend --> UI: Reservation confirmation
  UI --> User: Display reservation confirmation

  User -> UI: Request guidance
  UI -> Backend: Get route to parking space
  Backend -> DB: Get reserved parking space
  DB --> Backend: Parking space details
  Backend -> Backend: Calculate route from entry point
  Backend --> UI: Send route guidance
  UI --> User: Display route guidance

  User -> UI: Request checkout
  UI -> Backend: Calculate parking fee
  Backend -> DB: Get parking session and pricing policy
  DB --> Backend: Session and pricing details
  Backend -> Backend: Calculate total fee
  Backend --> UI: Return fee amount
  UI --> User: Display fee

  User -> UI: Confirm payment
  UI -> Backend: Process payment
  Backend -> Payment: Send payment request
  Payment --> Backend: Payment result

  alt Payment approved
    Backend -> DB: Save payment transaction
    Backend -> DB: Mark session completed
    DB --> Backend: Transaction saved
    Backend --> UI: Payment confirmation
    UI --> User: Display payment success
  else Payment failed
    Backend --> UI: Payment failure message
    UI --> User: Ask user to retry payment
  end
else No spaces available
  Backend --> UI: Parking full message
  UI --> User: Display parking full
end
@enduml
